




NB
  All real config files are outside of the repo
  /sample-configs/ are copies


Heroku
  Heroku automatic server initialization, crashes locally 
    npm run start

  Heroku local environment test
    npm run prod ../heroku-config.js

Local compile and launch
  Dev 
    npm run dev ../dev-config.js 
  
  Prod 
    npm run prod ../prod-config.js

TESTS
  Selenium
    terminal 1:  cd /
                 npm run dev /test-selenium/selenium-config.js

    terminal 2:  cd /test-selenium
                 node all-selenium-tests

                 node create-recipe/createRecipe_addComment_delRecipe.sel


  Vitest
    npx vitest /test-jsx-browser

    npx vitest /test-jsx-browser/redux-store/reduxChangeRecipe.test.mjs

  Mocha
    npm run test-node

    npm run test-single -- test-cjs-node/**/addComment.spec.cjs
  
  Storybook
    npm run storybook


















